title: PS Brush set #1 - Decorative Crests ~ Diva of Design
description:
Happy to present to you my first brush collection for Photoshop. Should work just fine in all versions of the program, and if you need help or not sure how to install brushes feel free to send me a PM. ~ DH

These decorative crests are extremely ornate and perfect for t-shirt designs, or to enhance your vector logos and illustrations. The download features the original vector illustration, plus grunge PS brushes versions as well.
